headline: IDEXX Laboratories to Release 2025 First Quarter Financial Results
summary: WESTBROOK, Maine, April 03, 2025--IDEXX Laboratories, Inc. (NASDAQ: IDXX), a global leader in pet healthcare innovation, has scheduled the release of its 2025 first quarter financial results for Thursday, May 1, 2025, before the market opens. The Company will conduct an analyst conference call beginning at 8:30 a.m. ET on that day.
